extendedInfo.description: Hello everyone. Thank you for downloading and installing my Forest Morning Live Wallpaper. Remember, that it's a free app, which you can download to your Android device as a Live Wallpaper.Installation is really easy: go to "Home screen" -> press "Menu" -> "Wallpapers" -> hit "LiveWallpapers"This way you'll see currently installed LWP, which you can install to your android powered device.This application was tested on all Samsung devices, including Nexus, Note, S2, S3 and S series.You can download it to Motorola, LG and HTC phones as well.Installed HD wallpaper will show you amazing set of pictures.Please, remember to vote and tell your friends about this wallpaper!
